snippet.textDisplay:
Waited so many years for a new Defender for North America, then this. Another over-done luxury SUV in a market glutted with luxury SUV's. Yeah, super tough and combat ready, with your $100 no spill dog bowl and luxurious appointments.
What a waste of time
How does it stand out, other than the price tag and pretentiousness? Certainly not in appearance. You may ooh and ahh over minor variations but it is no different than every other SUV out there.
THE DEFENDER, when soccer moms need to drop the kids off and get to pilates ASAP
